## Environment and commands

No Python environment required. CI is Markdown-only. Markdownlint rules: **`.markdownlint-cli2.yaml`** at the repo root.

```bash
npx --yes markdownlint-cli2 "README.md" "docs/**/*.md" "notes/**/*.md" "specs/**/*.md" "evals/**/*.md" "patterns/**/*.md" "experiments/**/*.md"
```

---

## Quality quick-check

- [ ] Topic files follow `NN_<slug>.md` naming within their folder
- [ ] Content is original synthesis with citations where needed
- [ ] No unauthorized reference to internal-only material in public docs
- [ ] First-person voice in notes; no instructor/course framing
